        <title>屏蔽Kodi的关机、重启按钮</title>
        <link>https://www.evine.win/p/%E5%B1%8F%E8%94%BDkodi%E7%9A%84%E5%85%B3%E6%9C%BA%E9%87%8D%E5%90%AF%E6%8C%89%E9%92%AE/</link>
